Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.26,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:15.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:23.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:27.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:34.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:38.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:45.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:52.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:56.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:04.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:08.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:15.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:19.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,160.389)}The Terrifying Operation: Pet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx140\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,730.389)}Rider S.O.S!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... you'll pay for your interference!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this monster to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what was that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin the next\Nphase of Operation: Pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are proceeding apace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezcondor will spread his\Nbacteria throughout Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and throw the citizens of\NTokyo into fear and unrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Within twenty-four hours—in other\Nwords, at this time tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo will be a wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, Tokyo will belong\Nto Gel Shocker, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It will be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezcondor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread your plague germs across Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the city into a wasteland!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Peel it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What could this disease be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a report from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been an outbreak\Nof plague in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The plague?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the people carrying the infected\Nto the hospital have come down with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At this right, the plague will\Nspread to all of Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe even all of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Rider Corps HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's been attacked\Nby a Gel Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Gel Shocker monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was already gone when we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hated enemy, Hongo\NTakeshi is flailing helplessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to wipe them out\Nwith a concentrated strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate phase two of Operation: Pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will send a cyborg\Ndirectly to Rider Corps HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish off Hongo and his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,by infecting them with the plague!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Cute, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy mice are genuinely charming and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A mouse wouldn't make a bad pet at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't he cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I watch it, the cuter he looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mouse remind you of someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just not coming to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect match!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who do you think\Nthis mouse looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A fancy mouse, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Very cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster we fought before, Nezcondor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked a bit like a mouse, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats spread the black plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that pet mouse might...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never heard of pet\Nmice spreading the plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what if Gel Shocker\Nis controlling the mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You... darn monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The mouse is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He runs fast. I'll give him that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, did he hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a tough monster\Nwe're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they tricked us like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black, that was\Na pathetic performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you simply helpless\Nbefore the Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've reviewed the reasons\Nfor Nezcondor's loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and equipped it with a more\Npowerful secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time before\Nthe Kamen Rider falls to Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If they create an effective vaccine,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they could overcome Nezcondor's\Nplague, too, couldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You should wait, sir, and watch\Nthe enhanced Nezcondor in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll spread even more powerful bacteria\Nand turn Tokyo into a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezcondor, show our leader your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come here and help me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:20.80,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A m-monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling... hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there any way to relieve\Nhis terror, at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him a tranquilizer,\Nbut it doesn't seem to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we found non-plague germs\Non the patient's fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-plague germs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a vaccine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment he was brought in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we got some corneas from the eye\Nbank and gave him a transplant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's acting so wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What he needs is rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. Another urgent patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even transport\Nour patients like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We need...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to beat Nezcondor\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A new antibiotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can make a vaccine\Nto resist the new bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to finish it as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The trains have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They think mice chewed through the cables.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Nezcondor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gouge out your eyes so\Nthat you can never fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll infect you with my bacteria,\Nand let you die an agonizing death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Mr. Takeshi be blind now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a scratch on the\Nsurface of my eyes, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But you need rest and\Nrelaxation until you heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't rest until I defeat Nezcondor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The vaccine will be finished soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Nezcondor to Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fancy mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something on its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it... it bit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Taki is in our custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi, if you wish to save Taki,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,come alone to the third sluice gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezcondor."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi, you need to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going in your condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if my\Nvision is compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can see a little, I can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:17:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't abandon Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... you're practically blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even see where Taki is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think you can\Nfight in your condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezcondor... you've underestimated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your poison won't affect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.51,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:57.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:04.30,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.86,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:11.32,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:15.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.59,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:22.31,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:26.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:36.79,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:43.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:47.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:50.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:58.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:01.44,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:05.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:09.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:23.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:26.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:30.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:34.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:37.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:44.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:48.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.74,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nezcondor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Lunar Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Nezcondor is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vaccine! The vaccine is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll fix your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:53.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's terrifying\NOperation: Pet was foiled,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:55.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and Hongo Takeshi's eyes were healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:58.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Gel Shocker would have more terrifying\Nmonsters waiting in the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:01.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:10.80,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:14.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:13.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Centipede Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:17.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker will form a Gel Shocker Kid Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:20.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to oppose the Kamen Rider Kid Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:22.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to be positioned all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:26.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If anyone resists us, burn them to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:29.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then we'll really make the Kamen Rider suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:31.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Centipede Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs98\bord0.8\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,730.389)}Enroll in the\NGel Shocker Terror School!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:39.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.22,0:23:42.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:46.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:50.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:54.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:24:01.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:06.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:12.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Terrifying Operation: Pet\NRider S.O.S!
Comment: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Enroll in the\NGel Shocker Terror School!!